{
  "stem": "19596.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke English a bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I came to his barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were separate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The fire brigade was in a separate barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard through somebody else, or we spoke together, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I can teach English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, that's good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Come to me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I came to him where he lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people didn't like that the Jew comes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some Polish people didn't like that the Jew comes, and-- and that's my daughter there in the back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some Jew didn't like that they come in the barracks, but he didn't care so I went there and spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave me half a bread extra.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had access.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and he always-- he liked me and we-- we became friendly, very friendly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was another one, Cholonowski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was number 45.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No, not 45. 145. 145.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He lives here in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also in the fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was also in the fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have been told some time on selections-- that means when they were selecting people in front of the block who were weak or things like that, they had to go in a truck and to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew about it before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always I had my information from them, from the fire brigade, that I tell others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of them were very good guys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I got onto a Kommando of butchers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The butchers, they were working in an SS kitchen, in an SS butchery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were making sausages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Salamis and-- and Polish shortages, all for the SS, for the troops.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
